<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Forgot Password Email</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
        }
        </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Please Reset your password</h1>
    <p>Hi {{name}},</p>
    <p>We have got a request to reset your password use the OTP below:</p>
    <p>OTP: {{otp}}</p>
    <p>This OTP is valid for {{otpExpiry}} minutes.</p>
    <p>If you did not request this, please ignore this email.</p>
    <p>Best regards,</p>
    <p>Pinntag Team</p>
</body>
</html>
